FPL CHALLENGE STUDIO — PHASE 6
================================

WHAT THIS UPDATE DOES
---------------------
Adds the Publishing Centre to the separate admin page. It does not edit or publish the live game automatically.

UPLOAD THESE FILES TO THE MAIN/ROOT OF YOUR GITHUB REPOSITORY
--------------------------------------------------------------
Replace:
- admin.html
- admin.css
- admin.js
- admin-phase3.js
- admin-phase5.js

Add:
- admin-phase6.js

KEEP THESE LIVE-GAME FILES UNCHANGED
------------------------------------
- index.html
- players.js
- todays-challenge.js
- prompt-library.js
- visuals.css

AFTER UPLOADING
---------------
1. Commit the files.
2. Wait for GitHub Pages to finish deploying.
3. Open admin.html.
4. Press Ctrl + F5.
5. The heading should say Challenge Studio · Phase 6.

PHASE 6 WORKFLOW
----------------
1. Generate and review the challenge.
2. Run the automatic Test Mode checks.
3. Record the tested challenge in Challenge History.
4. Scroll to Step 7 — Publishing Centre.
5. Review the live-versus-prepared comparison and checklist.
6. Download the publishing pack once it says Ready to upload.
7. Extract the pack and upload only UPLOAD/todays-challenge.js to GitHub.

The publishing pack also contains local backups of challenge history, the prompt library, and the live challenge file that was present before publishing.
